text: Nocardioides dokdonensis is a bacterium from the genus Nocardioides which has been isolated from sand sediments from the beach of the Dokdo Island in Korea . == References == ==External links== *Type strain of Nocardioides dokdonensis at BacDive - the Bacterial Diversity Metadatabase dokdonensis Category:Bacteria described in 2008
title: Nocardioides dokdonensis
